descriptionHtml:
Enjoy all the Real Valladolid information like never before.

Discover the latest Real Valladolid CF news, watch exclusive videos, check the calendar of events, standings and live scores. Analyze player stats, find out who is the top scorer of Pucela and compare all stats. Don't miss anything from our social networks in the only official Real Valladolid CF app.
Consult the map to access the stadium and its history. Access the best and most complete multimedia content and receive push notifications about the latest Real Valladolid news.

Receive alerts about goals, news, match schedules and statistics of your favorite players. Live all the excitement of LaLiga from your mobile totally free.
Features

✔ News: follow the latest Real Valladolid news, discover all the news, the latest signings, match results, and stay informed with the official releases from the Club and LaLiga. Keep up to date with the reactions of the protagonists of the matches of the day, interviews, and evaluations of the matches.

Multimedia: discover the videos of your Pucela. Relive all the goals and the best moments of the matches with the best multimedia content made just for you. Access to summaries in detail: goals, dribbles, saves, and the best plays of Real Valladolid, also from past seasons. Remember the most legendary plays and recall the best goals of your favorite players.

Calendar, results and live standings: check all the key dates and schedules in the official calendar for all Real Valladolid CF competitions: LaLiga, Copa del Rey,... All the matchdays with live results of each match and the general classification are completely updated. Follow instantly what is happening during all the matches with live updated information.

Average and details of all live matches. Find out who dominates possession of the ball at any given moment and access every detail of the matches easily.

Player statistics: access the statistics of all players and compare them with each other. The stats comparator will give you accurate data on goals, games, minutes played, yellow and red cards, assists, shots, dribbles, fouls, passes, crosses, tackles and much more on all Pucela players.

Push notifications: don't miss a single detail thanks to fully configurable push notifications. Receive live alerts of all the content.

Social Networks: follow all Real Valladolid CF social networks through the official app. Don't miss anything on our networks!

Information about the Municipal Stadium José Zorrilla: access the access map to the stadium and check all the related information. Take a guided tour of Zorrilla, check the schedules and means of transport.

Download it now for free.

Receive alerts about goals, news, match schedules and statistics of your favorite players. Live all the excitement of LaLiga from your mobile totally free.
Features

✔ News: follow the latest Real Valladolid news, discover all the news, the latest signings, match results, and stay informed with the official releases from the Club and LaLiga. Keep up to date with the reactions of the protagonists of the matches of the day, interviews, and evaluations of the matches.

Multimedia: discover the videos of your Pucela. Relive all the goals and the best moments of the matches with the best multimedia content made just for you. Access to summaries in detail: goals, dribbles, saves, and the best plays of Real Valladolid, also from past seasons. Remember the most legendary plays and recall the best goals of your favorite players.

Calendar, results and live standings: check all the key dates and schedules in the official calendar for all Real Valladolid CF competitions: LaLiga, Copa del Rey,... All the matchdays with live results of each match and the general classification are completely updated. Follow instantly what is happening during all the matches with live updated information.

Average and details of all live matches. Find out who dominates possession of the ball at any given moment and access every detail of the matches easily.

Player statistics: access the statistics of all players and compare them with each other. The stats comparator will give you accurate data on goals, games, minutes played, yellow and red cards, assists, shots, dribbles, fouls, passes, crosses, tackles and much more on all Pucela players.

Push notifications: don't miss a single detail thanks to fully configurable push notifications. Receive live alerts of all the content.

Social Networks: follow all Real Valladolid CF social networks through the official app. Don't miss anything on our networks!

Information about the Municipal Stadium José Zorrilla: access the access map to the stadium and check all the related information. Take a guided tour of Zorrilla, check the schedules and means of transport.
